This is a cross platform calculator project for learning/demonstrating the MonoDevelop Gtk# platform. 
It utilizes an event aggregator to "loosely couple the UI from the State" (because event aggregators are cool.)

Build instructions:
+ With Monodevelop
  -Pull in nuget packages
  -Confirm targeting Monodevelop runtime.
  -Rebuild all

+ With Visual Studio
  -Pull in nuget packages
  -Install Gtk# nuget package.
  -Replace mono specific code in the auto generated /gtk-gui/MainWindow.cs
  -Rebuild all
  
